sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as Transfer - Customer - Client
    participant Gateway as API Gateway
    participant AccountS as Account Service
    participant DB_Accts as Accounts DB

    Client->>Gateway: GET /accounts/{accountId}
    Gateway->>AccountS: Forward get account request
    AccountS->>DB_Accts: Query account by ID
    DB_Accts-->>AccountS: Account details
    AccountS-->>Gateway: Account information
    Gateway-->>Client: 200 OK (account details)
